(secondQuint)DiamondTemp Ablation System for the Treatment of Paroxysmal Atrial Fibrillation.

 The DIAMOND-AF study is a prospective, single blind, 1:1 randomized controlled study being performed at multiple centers in the United States, Canada and Europe.

 The study will evaluate the safety and effectiveness of the DiamondTemp System used for ablation in patients with paroxysmal atrial fibrillation (AF).

 Subjects will be randomized for treatment with either the DiamondTemp Ablation Catheter or the TactiCath cent Quartz Contact Force Ablation Catheter manufactured by Abbott.

 Patients will be followed for 12 months.

